headline: Georgia-Pacific, Greif, Silgan detailed layoff plans in May
summary: Amcor and International Paper also disclosed forthcoming changes as they integrate recent acquisitions. LanzaTech, which has worked to create material for use in plastic packaging, is cutting part of its Illinois workforce.
